*amnesia* is a **Live System** ([Live CD](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Live_CD),
[Live USB](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Live_USB)) aimed at preserving your
privacy and anonymity: 

* all outgoing connections to the Internet are forced to go through
  the Tor network
* no trace is left on local storage devices unless explicitely asked.

It has many other [[features]].

amnesia is [Free Software](http://www.gnu.org/philosophy/free-sw.html)
released under the GNU/GPL (version 3 or above).

**WARNING**: this is alpha software, do not rely on it for
strong anonymity!

